parse.title: List of towns and cities with 100,000 or more inhabitants/country: C

text.*:
This is a list of towns and cities in the world in alphabetical order, beginning with the letter C, by country believed to have 100,000 or more inhabitants. Unless otherwise noted, populations are based on 2006 United Nations estimates.
